ninja
------------------------------------------
Ninja is a small build system with a focus on speed.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-2.6.1-1
  libstdc++6-5.4.0-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  binutils-2.25-4
  cygport-0.23.0-1
  gcc-core-5.4.0-1
  gcc-g++-5.4.0-1
  python-2.7.12-1

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/ninja-build/ninja

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/ninja-build/ninja/archive/v1.7.2.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack ninja-1.7.2-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./ninja-1.7.2-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/ninja-1.7.2-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/ninja-1.7.2-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(ninja)
  /usr/bin/ninja.exe
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/ninja.README
  /usr/share/doc/ninja/COPYING
  /usr/share/doc/ninja/HACKING.md
  /usr/share/doc/ninja/README

------------------

